'''Duggan Station''' was an area of [[Bburru Station]]. The headquarters for [[CorDuro Shipping]] was located there. [[Port Duggan]] was a docking area here; one that the ''[[Jade Shadow]]'' used at one point in the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]].

